{"tid":308912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日都好想咬人同咬野","createTime":"2017-07-04T14:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T11:58:09.000Z","uid":27741,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d80292cbbd3013dea87c601f0b31a4d3fe5738e0","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"每次見到另一半都勁想咬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行行下會拎佢隻手黎咬 坐低就想咬膊頭、面同頸 仲有耳仔同頭髮都好想咬 但係驚嚇親佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時啲傻下傻下嘅朋友我都好想咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  試過唔小心獸性大發最後勁尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我會咬爛好多野 例如啲樽口 咬到枝飲筒好似溶左咁 <br />\n另外好多時見到啲野 例如睇展覽睇廣告<br />\n或者見到啲哥基個大屎忽<br />\n我第一下就係衡量嗰舊野有冇咬口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後就會好順口講左句：我真係好想咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fadfa3da59557085c2bf448f11df0d9601a14af","tid":308912,"uid":23236,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"你細細個一歲左右屋企人係咪唔係好點理你？"},{"pid":"65fadaad9da19379a447227fbd8ac0f63b79438d","tid":308912,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"想唔想咬撚"},{"pid":"5f50444157742d71070b81dd5c750f6f6a47d7e9","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你細細個一歲左右屋企人係咪唔係好點理你？</blockquote><br />\n一歲唔記得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關事？"},{"pid":"8f82c47f57ce5674757d0195d371c200fe61a90c","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想唔想咬撚</blockquote><br />\nGay ok? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138