slike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都好鐘意咬 發泡膠盒可以咬到碎哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日求男朋友俾我咬下巴仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又求家姐俾我咬小腿 但失敗咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發泡膠我一直想試但係唔敢咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚唔小心食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好想咬男朋友啊下巴啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果可以隨時隨地有得咬男朋友就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家姐應該會覺得你痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇啲咩咬過覺得好正返唔到轉頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想比你咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7140848128a346c3d4a9ff8a11b6d7c713c3d389","tid":308912,"uid":35749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"我成日都咬女朋友 成日俾佢鬧咬痛佢"},{"pid":"526411b70575d0f8018e9ee94a8f5b09826dcbf7","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日都咬女朋友 成日俾佢鬧咬痛佢</blockquote><br />\n你好大力咬？<br />\n其實我覺得控制力度好難<br />\n太輕力又冇口感 大力少少對方已經痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係大大力咬又好有滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160145e36bd89d7420cab62afcd61c6b0ab99268","tid":308912,"uid":84505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都好鐘意咬 發泡膠盒可以咬到碎哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日求男朋友俾我咬下巴仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又求家姐俾我咬小腿 但失敗咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發泡膠我一直想試但係唔敢咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚唔小心食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好想咬男朋友啊下巴啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果可以隨時隨地有得咬男朋友就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家姐應該會覺得你痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇啲咩咬過覺得好正返唔到轉頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要輕輕力咁咬 個質感應該都係返唔到轉頭之一<br />\n幾年前好on9咁因為發口痕買咗舊bb軟膠 但太硬唔好咬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時無聊會咬開汽水罐個舊鐵 其實好撚癲隨時吞咗<br />\n家姐瘋狂拒絕但好似已經習以為常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我痴線開<br />\n最正都真係下巴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者手臂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無得成日咬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c46617bc0a5013be094d2461db7714dcca7b235","tid":308912,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維尼好肉地應該都幾好咬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪a你 我報警tim a"},{"pid":"a54c61d76c88292fdff48b6809774a855a177feb","tid":308912,"uid":99048,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"口欲期沒有得到滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016b83dedee6941424165d34fc7ceb9987668aee","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都好鐘意咬 發泡膠盒可以咬到碎哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日求男朋友俾我咬下巴仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又求家姐俾我咬小腿 但失敗咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發泡膠我一直想試但係唔敢咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚唔小心食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好想咬男朋友啊下巴啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果可以隨時隨地有得咬男朋友就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家姐應該會覺得你痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇啲咩咬過覺得好正返唔到轉頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要輕輕力咁咬 個質感應該都係返唔到轉頭之一<br />\n幾年前好on9咁因為發口痕買咗舊bb軟膠 但太硬唔好咬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時無聊會咬開汽水罐個舊鐵 其實好撚癲隨時吞咗<br />\n家姐瘋狂拒絕但好似已經習以為常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我痴線開<br />\n最正都真係下巴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者手臂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無得成日咬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到咬野都有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b940e8da18a6b31a35eed1aa91d6d0af2cb86b","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>畜牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n維尼好肉地應該都幾好咬</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪a你 我報警tim a</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大大啖"},{"pid":"d39cba21a64988d7d81382f1d7f4de614e344396","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>口欲期沒有得到滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪同上面個巴打問我細個係咪冇人理有關？"},{"pid":"c565514e3dd4a0cdc04d712352bbefee01621969","tid":308912,"uid":102641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"港女扮可愛？"},{"pid":"3e1d13551914ed5944f2301700aa85678b83b7c9","tid":308912,"uid":49815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"成日咬自己隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5174bec68b5e7ac4216b6f77a629a728727bede","tid":308912,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:50:35.000